Question

Consider the \(L\)-system (and angle) defined below:

  • Start: A
  • Rules:
    A > B+B+B+B+B
    B > [-CCA]BB
    C > CC
  • Number of recursions (number of iterations):
    • 5
  • Angle
    • 72

Please use this online tool to generate the pattern.


Answerlist

  • A
  • B
  • C
  • D
  • E
  • F
  • G
  • H

Solution

The correct pattern is pattern C.

  1. Use the first link: https://draemm.li/various/fractals/l-systems/
  2. Copy/paste the Start, Rules, Angle, and Recursions.
  3. I usually start Distance at 1. It can be less than 1, like 0.1, if needed.
  4. Click Run!
  5. If necessary to make the pattern centered and scaled, adjust the Start pos, Start angle, and Distance.
  6. Back to the quiz, select the matching pattern.
